data.description:
Prepare to be wowed by this radiant and spacious 3-bedroom gem nestled within the sought-after Forest Hills School District! The heart of the home, a stunning open kitchen, boasts brand-new cabinets, sleek stainless-steel appliances, a stylish tile backsplash, and exquisite quartz countertops.

Step into the expansive main level that effortlessly flows into a grand great room adorned with a cozy fireplace, seamlessly connected to a delightful 3-season sunroom—perfect for basking in the sun's warmth.

Ascending to the upper level, discover three generously-sized bedrooms and a pristine main bathroom. The lower level surprises with a versatile flex room, a convenient half-bathroom, a laundry room, and easy access to the attached heated 1-car garage. Need more space? The basement awaits as a blank canvas for a workshop or extra storage. Revel in the recent upgrades, including fresh flooring on the main level, plush new carpeting downstairs, and beautifully refinished original hardwood floors upstairs.

This home is move-in ready, boasting newer mechanicals and a solid roof. Updated lighting, an attached garage, and a storage shed are among the added perks. Tucked away on a peaceful street mere steps from Cascade Township's Burton Park, this residence is the epitome of convenience and tranquility.

Enjoy close proximity to shopping, river access, recreational opportunities, and top-notch schools. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to embrace the Cascade/Ada lifestyle! Seller will review any and all offers on Saturday December 16th at 5:00pm.
